(89, 31, 'Maximus - Responsive Multi-Purpose Website Templat', '&lt;p&gt;\r\n	&lt;strong style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 13px; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(52, 52, 52); line-height: 19px;&quot;&gt;Maximus is a responsive multipurpose website template, professional template suitable for any business or portfolio, and it&amp;rsquo;s created by using the latest HTML5 and CSS3 techniques. With a responsive design it is easily usable with any device (Desktop, Ipad, mobile phone&amp;hellip;), without removing any content.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', '/items/2012/11/89/preview/6eaf7245cff554db20863a7d88958553.png.png', '/items/2012/11/89/preview/6eaf7245cff554db20863a7d88958553.png.png', '/items/2012/11/89/6f052dfc2713076606250e5828d49d64.zip', '/items/2012/11/89/6f052dfc2713076606250e5828d49d64.zip', 'sample image.zip', NULL, 'http://www.okathemes.com/themes/maximus/index.html', 14, 14, 1, 9.1, 4, 1, 4, 0, 'true', 'true', '0000-00-00', '0000-00-00', NULL, '2012-11-09 18:45:12', 'active', 'themes', '', '', 0),
(90, 31, 'Dardania - News &amp; blog HTML', '&lt;p style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 13px; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 19px; &quot;&gt;\r\n	You can see the pages below on &amp;ldquo;pages&amp;rdquo; in the main menu. Hompage, Article view, Category view 1, Category view 2, Typography, Elements, Buttons.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 13px; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 19px; &quot;&gt;\r\n	14 HTML documents - Lite version - Dark version&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 13px; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 19px; &quot;&gt;\r\n	This theme is usable for blogs, magazines, newspapers, tv channels etc.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', '/items/2012/11/90/preview/799cb28e951e0abd91d1053ca7836cee.png.png', '/items/2012/11/90/preview/799cb28e951e0abd91d1053ca7836cee.png.png', '/items/2012/11/90/c648f0aa72306aeae3e5ff8201163318.zip', '/items/2012/11/90/c648f0aa72306aeae3e5ff8201163318.zip', 'sample image.zip', NULL, 'http://themeforest.net/item/dardania-news-blog-html/full_screen_preview/3285836', 15, 15, 2, 1500, 3, 16, 54, 0, 'false', 'false', '0000-00-00', '0000-00-00', NULL, '2012-11-09 18:47:51', 'extended_buy', 'themes', '', '', 0),
(91, 4, 'NewsSetter - News, Technology &amp; Reviews HTML T', '&lt;p style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 13px; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 19px;&quot;&gt;\r\n	This magazine HTML theme will be perfect for your technology reviews or gadget articles website. Oozing modern design, this responsive theme is a pleasure to use and to look at.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 13px; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 19px;&quot;&gt;\r\n	The HTML theme sports a few different styles of headers, 4 specially made colour variations. Also, the &amp;ldquo;Review&amp;rdquo; pages are a sight to behold, because of their nice flowing layout and modern style. Of course, there are short codes available and many more useful pages that make this theme one of our most complete one to date.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 13px; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 19px; &quot;&gt;\r\n	Read FAQ for more details&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', '/items/2012/11/91/preview/247a47a31c505c7f7c0f4c85904960d1.png', '/items/2012/11/91/preview/247a47a31c505c7f7c0f4c85904960d1.png', '/items/2012/11/91/88fa227faca057f603283f7720388992.zip', '/items/2012/11/91/88fa227faca057f603283f7720388992.zip', 'sample image.zip', NULL, 'http://themefuse.com/demo/html/NewsSetter/Black/index.html', 20, 20, 5, 2039, 3, 17, 55, -2, 'false', 'false', '0000-00-00', '0000-00-00', NULL, '2012-11-09 18:52:24', 'active', 'themes', '', '', 0),
(132, 31, 'Super Skeleton WP', '&lt;div&gt;\r\n	&lt;font color=&quot;#3c3c3b&quot; face=&quot;Verdana, Arial&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12px;&quot;&gt;Our Flagship Responsive Theme!&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;div&gt;\r\n	&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;div&gt;\r\n	&lt;font color=&quot;#3c3c3b&quot; face=&quot;Verdana, Arial&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12px;&quot;&gt;Update November 12th, 2012: Version 2.0.5 is out with lots of new speed and SEO and speed features! It&amp;rsquo;s FASTER now! The finished theme loads in under 0.5 seconds when hosted with WPEngine.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;div&gt;\r\n	&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;div&gt;\r\n	&lt;font color=&quot;#3c3c3b&quot; face=&quot;Verdana, Arial&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12px;&quot;&gt;Designed for basic users, not geeks &amp;ndash; all by a dude in Southern California who just loves making rockin&amp;rsquo; WP themes for other folks.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;div&gt;\r\n	&lt;font color=&quot;#3c3c3b&quot; face=&quot;Verdana, Arial&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12px;&quot;&gt;There&amp;rsquo;s a dedicated support forum based on the super cool Ticksy support system! Just file a ticket and we&amp;rsquo;ll get back to you pronto!&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;div&gt;\r\n	&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;div&gt;\r\n	&lt;div&gt;\r\n		&lt;font color=&quot;#3c3c3b&quot; face=&quot;Verdana, Arial&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12px;&quot;&gt;SuperSkeleton for WordPress is responsive (try resizing your browser)... that means that it&amp;rsquo;ll flex to fit massive screens, or itty bitty iPhone screens (and everything in between). Touch gestures even work on the slider!&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n	&lt;div&gt;\r\n		&lt;font color=&quot;#3c3c3b&quot; face=&quot;Verdana, Arial&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12px;&quot;&gt;SuperSkeleton is more than a WordPress theme, it&amp;rsquo;s a comprehensive HTML5 framework and it includes a full templating system as well; A collection of several incredibly powerful scripts and CSS structures that&amp;rsquo;s been tied together into a kit that&amp;rsquo;s perfect as a jumping off point of your next project.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n	&lt;div&gt;\r\n		&lt;font color=&quot;#3c3c3b&quot; face=&quot;Verdana, Arial&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12px;&quot;&gt;We&amp;rsquo;ve got SEO and other fancy search engine optimization tricks baked into the theme as well&amp;hellip; so it&amp;rsquo;ll get crawled well and people can find ya easier! There&amp;rsquo;s even some social stuff included as well! It&amp;rsquo;s all built on the SuperSkeleton theme system &amp;ndash; a robust, flexible, magically delicious system that&amp;rsquo;s collected nearly 6,000 sales in just a couple months!&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n	&lt;div&gt;\r\n		&lt;font color=&quot;#3c3c3b&quot; face=&quot;Verdana, Arial&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12px;&quot;&gt;Oh, and the markup, it&amp;rsquo;s fully standards compliant and written in a way that&amp;rsquo;s easy to understand. No messy naming silliness&amp;hellip; just simple, semantic class names that anyone can understand within minutes. Heck, it&amp;rsquo;s based on the popular 960.gs, so unless you&amp;rsquo;ve been living under a rock, you know this is going to be pretty simple to use.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n	&lt;div&gt;\r\n		&lt;font color=&quot;#3c3c3b&quot; face=&quot;Verdana, Arial&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12px;&quot;&gt;SuperSkeleton is well organized. Take what you love, leave what you don&amp;rsquo;t, customize the rest. It&amp;rsquo;s completely in your hands &amp;ndash; turn it into the next big thing, or just as your little personal projects, it&amp;rsquo;s up to you.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n	&lt;div&gt;\r\n		&lt;font color=&quot;#3c3c3b&quot; face=&quot;Verdana, Arial&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12px;&quot;&gt;What&amp;rsquo;s Included?&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n	&lt;div&gt;\r\n		&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n	&lt;div&gt;\r\n		&lt;font color=&quot;#3c3c3b&quot; face=&quot;Verdana, Arial&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12px;&quot;&gt;Fully Responsive WordPress Theme and Theme-Options Manager&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n	&lt;div&gt;\r\n		&lt;font color=&quot;#3c3c3b&quot; face=&quot;Verdana, Arial&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12px;&quot;&gt;SEO / SEM &amp;ndash; Search Engine Optimized and Ready for Marketing&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n	&lt;div&gt;\r\n		&lt;font color=&quot;#3c3c3b&quot; face=&quot;Verdana, Arial&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12px;&quot;&gt;20 Bonus HTML Template Files (showcasing the flexibility of the framework)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n	&lt;div&gt;\r\n		&lt;font color=&quot;#3c3c3b&quot; face=&quot;Verdana, Arial&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12px;&quot;&gt;The Super Skeleton UI Kit (Exclusive Freebie PSD )&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n	&lt;div&gt;\r\n		&lt;font color=&quot;#3c3c3b&quot; face=&quot;Verdana, Arial&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12px;&quot;&gt;3 Minimal skins and 2 fontstacks to start with. (Adding 100+ skins is really silly if you ask me &amp;nbsp;)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n	&lt;div&gt;\r\n		&lt;font color=&quot;#3c3c3b&quot; face=&quot;Verdana, Arial&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12px;&quot;&gt;Fully internationalized and ready for translation!&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n	&lt;div&gt;\r\n		&lt;font color=&quot;#3c3c3b&quot; face=&quot;Verdana, Arial&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12px;&quot;&gt;Individual Skinnable PSD files for all major UI elements&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n	&lt;div&gt;\r\n		&lt;font color=&quot;#3c3c3b&quot; face=&quot;Verdana, Arial&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12px;&quot;&gt;Organized CSS files, including easy to use Media-Queries sections.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n	&lt;div&gt;\r\n		&lt;font color=&quot;#3c3c3b&quot; face=&quot;Verdana, Arial&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12px;&quot;&gt;Filterable Portfolio/Gallery system&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n	&lt;div&gt;\r\n		&lt;font color=&quot;#3c3c3b&quot; face=&quot;Verdana, Arial&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12px;&quot;&gt;Non-Obtrusive Javascript. All major site elements work even on old browsers.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n	&lt;div&gt;\r\n		&lt;font color=&quot;#3c3c3b&quot; face=&quot;Verdana, Arial&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12px;&quot;&gt;The basics: lightbox, image overlay effects, CSS3 (coded to work or degrade gracefully on old browsers), form elements, brandable footer, etc. Everything you would expect from a premium HTML framework.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n	&lt;div&gt;\r\n		&lt;font color=&quot;#3c3c3b&quot; face=&quot;Verdana, Arial&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12px;&quot;&gt;Extensive Documentation&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n', '/items/2012/11/132/preview/12e78178c96bd3177573985886c94226.png', '/items/2012/11/132/preview/12e78178c96bd3177573985886c94226.png', '/items/2012/11/132/99e2ebb3e44b777323c9f7bd155600c6.zip', '/items/2012/11/132/99e2ebb3e44b777323c9f7bd155600c6.zip', 'file.zip', NULL, 'http://super-skeleton.mdnw.net/', 45, 45, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'false', 'false', '0000-00-00', '0000-00-00', 'blabla', '2012-11-29 15:45:15', 'active', 'themes', '', '', 0),
(133, 31, 'Rockit Now', '&lt;div style=&quot;font-weight: normal;&quot;&gt;\r\n	Rockit Now is a wordpress theme specially designed for Bands and music websites. This template&amp;nbsp;is easy to modify and ready to be up and running out of the box. The PSD files included have&amp;nbsp;been customized to allow fast skinning.&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;div style=&quot;font-weight: normal;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;div&gt;\r\n	&lt;b&gt;Main Features&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;div style=&quot;font-weight: normal;&quot;&gt;\r\n	Event Managment&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;div style=&quot;font-weight: normal;&quot;&gt;\r\n	Gallery Managment&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;div style=&quot;font-weight: normal;&quot;&gt;\r\n	Album + Track Managment&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;div style=&quot;font-weight: normal;&quot;&gt;\r\n	Slider Managment&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;div style=&quot;font-weight: normal;&quot;&gt;\r\n	Sidebar Managment&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;div style=&quot;font-weight: normal;&quot;&gt;\r\n	Powerfull Theme Options + Page Builder&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;div style=&quot;font-weight: normal;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;div style=&quot;font-weight: normal;&quot;&gt;\r\n	This template comes in 8 pre made color variations. It will only take one minute to&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;div style=&quot;font-weight: normal;&quot;&gt;\r\n	create your desired color schemes by using theme options.&lt;/div&gt;\r\n', '/items/2012/11/133/preview/12d64dcaa78c78c5309b4fab95551dea.png.png', '/items/2012/11/133/preview/12d64dcaa78c78c5309b4fab95551dea.png.png', '/items/2012/11/133/dc385bf4b5d4f7a448d16a8ee6b81c2c.zip', '/items/2012/11/133/dc385bf4b5d4f7a448d16a8ee6b81c2c.zip', 'file.zip', NULL, 'http://chimpstudio.co.uk/wp-demo/rockit-update/', 45, 45, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'false', 'false', '0000-00-00', '0000-00-00', 'ajde', '2012-11-29 15:50:42', 'active', 'themes', '', '', 0),
(134, 31, 'Yin &amp; Yang', '&lt;div&gt;\r\n	Yin &amp;amp; Yang is a light, minimalistic, simple to use portfolio theme. Quick to setup and easy to customize, thanks to the powerful admin panel, and the detailed documentation, Yin &amp;amp; Yang is the perfect theme for showcasing your most important work directly in front of your potential clients.&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;div&gt;\r\n	Yin &amp;amp; Yang has got you covered on all fronts, so if you ever get stuck on anything, rest assured that you&amp;rsquo;re going to get the help of a professional, if and when you need it, because Yin &amp;amp; Yang comes with excellent customer support.&lt;/div&gt;\r\n', '/items/2012/11/134/preview/550af23af357131f11f764607335d551.png', '/items/2012/11/134/preview/550af23af357131f11f764607335d551.png', '/items/2012/11/134/38a4aa1a30e83d7fdcbc6e919c5edddd.zip', '/items/2012/11/134/38a4aa1a30e83d7fdcbc6e919c5edddd.zip', 'file.zip', NULL, 'http://onioneyethemes.com/yin-and-yang/', 45, 45, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'false', 'false', '0000-00-00', '0000-00-00', 'nema', '2012-11-29 15:54:25', 'active', 'themes', '', '', 0),
(135, 31, 'Muzak', '&lt;div&gt;\r\n	&lt;font color=&quot;#3c3c3b&quot; face=&quot;Verdana, Arial&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12px;&quot;&gt;Meet Muzak. A WordPress themes for bands, musicians, djs and everyone involved in the music business. But let&amp;rsquo;s take a look at the features of Muzak.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;div&gt;\r\n	&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;div&gt;\r\n	&lt;font color=&quot;#3c3c3b&quot; face=&quot;Verdana, Arial&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12px;&quot;&gt;1. Events Management&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;div&gt;\r\n	&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;div&gt;\r\n	&lt;font color=&quot;#3c3c3b&quot; face=&quot;Verdana, Arial&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12px;&quot;&gt;With Muzak you can display your upcoming events in a really nice way. You can also display them on a map (you can turn this off from our Theme Settings Panel) and past events (Also can be turned off)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;div&gt;\r\n	&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;div&gt;\r\n	&lt;font color=&quot;#3c3c3b&quot; face=&quot;Verdana, Arial&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12px;&quot;&gt;2. Discography Management&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;div&gt;\r\n	&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;div&gt;\r\n	&lt;font color=&quot;#3c3c3b&quot; face=&quot;Verdana, Arial&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12px;&quot;&gt;In Muzak you have the ability to share your music with your fans using either self hosted audio files (using JWPlayer) or embedded sounds from SoundCloud. A lot more information about your albums / music can be added via Discography settings.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;div&gt;\r\n	&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;div&gt;\r\n	&lt;font color=&quot;#3c3c3b&quot; face=&quot;Verdana, Arial&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12px;&quot;&gt;3. Videos Management&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;div&gt;\r\n	&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;div&gt;\r\n	&lt;font color=&quot;#3c3c3b&quot; face=&quot;Verdana, Arial&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12px;&quot;&gt;Want to share videos with your fans? No problem. You can again share videos either self-hosted or from services like Youtube, Vimeo etc.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n', '/items/2012/11/135/preview/4f1289d035b8ebb7a045b0fd10a8c400.png.png', '/items/2012/11/135/preview/4f1289d035b8ebb7a045b0fd10a8c400.png.png', '/items/2012/11/135/ac214ac6efdead5da693b5b9fd83992c.zip', '/items/2012/11/135/ac214ac6efdead5da693b5b9fd83992c.zip', 'file.zip', NULL, 'http://www.cssigniter.com/muzak2/', 50, 50, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'false', 'false', '0000-00-00', '0000-00-00', 'grtnen', '2012-11-29 15:59:41', 'active', 'themes', '', '', 0),
(136, 31, 'COSMOX', '&lt;div&gt;\r\n	COSMOX is a new era of WordPress theme. You can discover many new awesome features in this theme. For example &amp;lsquo;Page Builder&amp;rsquo;, it allow you to create page easily by drag-drop module. Moreover, it comes with many options on that. Also, to change color elements, it won&amp;rsquo;t be a big deal anymore, with our new admin panel, you can access to almost of all elements color. Admin panel in this theme is a real feature rich. You can also create unlimited sidebar, choosing over 500+ fonts or use your own custom font. We provide a custom font uploader.&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;div&gt;\r\n	COSMOX has 10 predefined color/theme options layouts that you may use for different purposes. One click switch layout options plus create your own layout. COSMOX is powerful multipurpose theme that will help you to build any site.&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;div&gt;\r\n	WPML and Localization Supported (We already prepare .pot and .mo files).&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;div&gt;\r\n	&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;div&gt;\r\n	SEO . We use heading tag(H1, H2, H3,&amp;hellip;) for title which is good practice for search engine site. Main contents are moved above sidebars (including both sidebar layout), now search engine will easily fine your main contents first. Also, &amp;lsquo;alt&amp;rsquo; tag for images is supported. This is also help search engine to analyst your site easily.&lt;/div&gt;\r\n', '/items/2012/11/136/preview/4a8919cd16d2cf80f74a89b6de43417f.png', '/items/2012/11/136/preview/4a8919cd16d2cf80f74a89b6de43417f.png', '/items/2012/11/136/8ba114390afc54a396751f334c50f2f3.zip', '/items/2012/11/136/8ba114390afc54a396751f334c50f2f3.zip', 'file.zip', NULL, 'http://cosmox.ozythemes.com/theme_select/', 55, 55, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'false', 'false', '0000-00-00', '0000-00-00', '', '2012-11-29 16:06:27', 'active', 'themes', '', '', 0),
(137, 31, 'Mila ', '&lt;p&gt;\r\n	&lt;font color=&quot;#3c3c3b&quot; face=&quot;Verdana, Arial&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12px;&quot;&gt;Mila is a masonry based Wordpress Theme optimized for a nice and good User Experience. Mila uses a smooth loading action to show off your pages which you can deactivate at any time. With the Theme Options, you can easily adapt the different page layouts to your needs.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', '/items/2012/11/137/preview/6de1712c1ef5c208551a2e7f9f99c995.png.png', '/items/2012/11/137/preview/6de1712c1ef5c208551a2e7f9f99c995.png.png', '/items/2012/11/137/10292baaaab34c8e87b8fd3196f67fb6.zip', '/items/2012/11/137/10292baaaab34c8e87b8fd3196f67fb6.zip', 'file.zip', NULL, 'http://spab-rice.com/wordpress/mila/', 40, 40, 1, 40, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'false', 'false', '0000-00-00', '0000-00-00', '', '2012-11-29 16:09:16', 'active', 'themes', '', '', 0),
(146, 31, 'Soundboard - a Premium Music WordPress Theme', '&lt;div&gt;\r\n	Soundboard is a powerful music WordPress theme with special features for bands and solo artists. With Soundboard you can display your tour dates, discography, videos and images &amp;ndash; it has pretty much everything you need for a band website.&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;div&gt;\r\n	This theme is all about your fans. Next to the news section your fans will find all the important stuff right on the homepage thanks to 7 custom widgets: upcoming tour dates, newest album, latest pictures, latest videos, twitter feed, ...&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;div&gt;\r\n	Soundboard is easy to use, even for users with no coding knowledge. If you are a professional designer and you are putting together a site for a band, this is something that you should check out as well. The simplicity of use and the special features make this theme so easy to get set up and running.&lt;/div&gt;\r\n', '/items/2012/11/146/9cde7f15af7baf24f434b1fe68cb90d6.png', '/items/2012/11/146/preview/9cde7f15af7baf24f434b1fe68cb90d6.png', '/items/2012/11/146/5d8ef48fd6abd832c15e95c7b03b70eb.zip', '/items/2012/11/146/5d8ef48fd6abd832c15e95c7b03b70eb.zip', NULL, NULL, 'http://www.themes.red-sun-design.com/soundboard/', 45, 45, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'false', 'false', '0000-00-00', '0000-00-00', '', '2012-11-30 09:57:53', 'active', 'themes', '', '', 0),
(139, 31, 'Daisho', '&lt;p&gt;\r\n	&lt;font color=&quot;#3c3c3b&quot; face=&quot;Verdana, Arial&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12px;&quot;&gt;Daisho is a portfolio solution for creative professionals and companies looking for a minimal and professional look. Flexible and responsive presentation, smooth navigational flow and clutter-free approach. Put your works in focus. Powerful Typography Plugin included. The definitive portfolio solution for creative professionals available now.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', '/items/2012/11/139/preview/efd106af83c85f1599cd01c36e335e4e.png', '/items/2012/11/139/preview/efd106af83c85f1599cd01c36e335e4e.png', '/items/2012/11/139/52167131064f3c56fd0cf36f3c9fc0ba.zip', '/items/2012/11/139/52167131064f3c56fd0cf36f3c9fc0ba.zip', 'file.zip', NULL, 'http://themes.devatic.com/daisho/', 45, 45, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'false', 'false', '0000-00-00', '0000-00-00', 'dasva', '2012-11-29 16:28:31', 'active', 'themes', '', '', 0),
(140, 31, 'King Size', '&lt;div&gt;\r\n	&lt;b&gt;PERFECT FOR VARIETY OF PURPOSES&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;div style=&quot;font-weight: normal;&quot;&gt;\r\n	Also available as an HTML Template, King Size makes perfect for a variety of purposes, although focused towards Photographers and those using Portfolios to display their past and present work collections.&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;div style=&quot;font-weight: normal;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;div&gt;\r\n	&lt;b&gt;HIGHLY CUSTOMIZABLE&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;div style=&quot;font-weight: normal;&quot;&gt;\r\n	Including a variety of options, King Size can be suitable to fit any particular use. Offering you five very different gallery styles (including 4 additional layout styles for ColorBox, FancyBox and prettyPhoto), with ability to blog about your photos (attach featured images) and etc.&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;div style=&quot;font-weight: normal;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;div&gt;\r\n	&lt;b&gt;GALLERY MANAGEMENT HAS NEVER BEEN SO EASY&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;div style=&quot;font-weight: normal;&quot;&gt;\r\n	Creating a Gallery or Portfolio can&amp;rsquo;t be any easier. You just upload your images via Media Gallery (all explained in the documentation) and automatically those images are converted to the Gallery Type you have selected for that specific page. There are no extra steps, just upload your images and click publish.&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;div style=&quot;font-weight: normal;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;div&gt;\r\n	&lt;b&gt;EXTENDED HELP DOCUMENTATION WITH VIDEO TUTORIALS&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;div style=&quot;font-weight: normal;&quot;&gt;\r\n	Well documented and user-friendly, also including 8 video tutorials to walk you through a variety of steps (although we must apologize for the sound-quality, these will be fixed soon). If at any time you&amp;rsquo;re stumped by something contact us; we&amp;rsquo;re here to help.&lt;/div&gt;\r\n', '/items/2012/11/140/preview/d09f3cfbfd09d1e55287e29964c5c3b2.png.png', '/items/2012/11/140/preview/d09f3cfbfd09d1e55287e29964c5c3b2.png.png', '/items/2012/11/140/9e17bb8b55daa6c1d8e32cde29135a2e.zip', '/items/2012/11/140/9e17bb8b55daa6c1d8e32cde29135a2e.zip', 'file.zip', NULL, 'http://www.kingsizetheme.com/', 55, 50, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'false', 'false', '0000-00-00', '0000-00-00', 'sebsr', '2012-11-29 16:32:28', 'active', 'themes', '', '', 0),
