(179, 31, 'Sellegance - Responsive and Clean OpenCart Theme', '&lt;h2&gt;\r\n	&lt;font color=&quot;#3c3c3b&quot; face=&quot;Verdana, Arial&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12px;&quot;&gt;Responsive and clean design for any kind of webshop&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;\r\n&lt;div&gt;\r\n	&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;div&gt;\r\n	&lt;font color=&quot;#3c3c3b&quot; face=&quot;Verdana, Arial&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12px;&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;NEW!&lt;/b&gt; version 1.4.3.1 Check details and update instructions here: &lt;a href=&quot;http://goo.gl/nIskC&quot;&gt;http://goo.gl/nIskC&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;div&gt;\r\n	&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;div&gt;\r\n	&lt;font color=&quot;#3c3c3b&quot; face=&quot;Verdana, Arial&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12px;&quot;&gt;NOTE: If you are using cloud zoom and want to upgrade to the newest release change your Additional Product Image size to 62&amp;times;62.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;div&gt;\r\n	&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;h2&gt;\r\n	&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12px; color: rgb(60, 60, 59); font-family: Verdana, Arial;&quot;&gt;IMPORTANT . The package still contains the legacy versions for 1.5.1.2 and 1.5.1.3 but they aren&amp;rsquo;t updated.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;\r\n&lt;div&gt;\r\n	&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;div&gt;\r\n	&lt;font color=&quot;#3c3c3b&quot; face=&quot;Verdana, Arial&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12px;&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;Sellegance is a responsive, elegant and easy to install OpenCart theme.&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;div&gt;\r\n	&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;div&gt;\r\n	&lt;font color=&quot;#3c3c3b&quot; face=&quot;Verdana, Arial&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12px;&quot;&gt;Choose your own colors and upload custom backgrounds directly from the admin panel.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;div&gt;\r\n	&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;div&gt;\r\n	&lt;font color=&quot;#3c3c3b&quot; face=&quot;Verdana, Arial&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12px;&quot;&gt;With its clean design and lots of features, you will have a very profitable online shop in no time.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;div&gt;\r\n	&lt;font color=&quot;#3c3c3b&quot; face=&quot;Verdana, Arial&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12px;&quot;&gt;It&amp;rsquo;s perfect for any kind of web shop. Its superb UI delivers the ultimate experience for end users. It has been built with mobile users in mind. So it &lt;b&gt;looks great on desktops, tablets and mobiles.&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;div&gt;\r\n	&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;div&gt;\r\n	&lt;font color=&quot;#3c3c3b&quot; face=&quot;Verdana, Arial&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12px;&quot;&gt;Every detail of registered users and affiliates panel has been carefully designed to fit the elegant design. Special care has been taken in the shopping cart and checkout to give you&lt;b&gt; high conversion rates&lt;/b&gt;, while retaining the whole great design.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;div&gt;\r\n	&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;div&gt;\r\n	&lt;font color=&quot;#3c3c3b&quot; face=&quot;Verdana, Arial&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12px;&quot;&gt;You don&amp;rsquo;t need any HTML /CSS knowledge to install this theme. Just upload and enable the theme and module, that&amp;rsquo;s all.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;div&gt;\r\n	&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;div&gt;\r\n	&lt;font color=&quot;#3c3c3b&quot; face=&quot;Verdana, Arial&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12px;&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;If you like the theme, don&amp;rsquo;t forget to rate it!&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;div&gt;\r\n	&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;h2&gt;\r\n	&lt;font color=&quot;#3c3c3b&quot; face=&quot;Verdana, Arial&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12px;&quot;&gt;Main Features&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;\r\n