div style=&quot;font-weight: normal;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;div style=&quot;font-weight: normal;&quot;&gt;\r\n	- Roundabout &amp;ldquo;Featured product&amp;rdquo; slider with autoplay function, Next and Previous navigation buttons and pause on hover.&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;div style=&quot;font-weight: normal;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;div style=&quot;font-weight: normal;&quot;&gt;\r\n	- Unique design with jQuery powered effects on almost every page.&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;div style=&quot;font-weight: normal;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;div style=&quot;font-weight: normal;&quot;&gt;\r\n	- Sticky side box for Cart module, Languages, Currencies and Search box.&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;div style=&quot;font-weight: normal;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;div style=&quot;font-weight: normal;&quot;&gt;\r\n	- SEO friendly page structure and code.&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;div style=&quot;font-weight: normal;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;div&gt;\r\n	&lt;b&gt;Integrated Social networking features:&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;div&gt;\r\n	&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;div style=&quot;font-weight: normal;&quot;&gt;\r\n	- Google +1 button, Twitter share button and Facebook like button in footer and additional share/like buttons for every product page.&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;div style=&quot;font-weight: normal;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;div style=&quot;font-weight: normal;&quot;&gt;\r\n	- Custom twitter feed slider&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;div style=&quot;font-weight: normal;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;div style=&quot;font-weight: normal;&quot;&gt;\r\n	The theme also have an advanced Facebook like box feature. When FB ID is used in the theme options panel, the like button in footer hides and a custom styled Like box appear next to the Google+ and Twitter buttons.&lt;/div&gt;\r\n', '/items/2012/12/180/Spicylicious.jpg', '/items/2012/12/180/Spicylicious.jpg', '/items/2012/12/180/4da25a5aed375d9f64