(181, 31, 'ShopCart - OpenCart theme with powerful options', '&lt;div&gt;\r\n	&lt;font color=&quot;#3c3c3b&quot; face=&quot;Verdana, Arial&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12px;&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;Updated to 1.5.2.1 / 1.5.3.1 / 1.5.4.1&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;div&gt;\r\n	&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;h2&gt;\r\n	&lt;font color=&quot;#3c3c3b&quot; face=&quot;Verdana, Arial&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12px;&quot;&gt;This theme is fully compatible with OpenCart 1.5.1.1 / 1.5.1.2 / 1.5.1.3/ 1.5.2.1 / 1.5.3.1/ 1.5.4.1&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;\r\n&lt;div&gt;\r\n	&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;h2&gt;\r\n	&lt;font color=&quot;#3c3c3b&quot; face=&quot;Verdana, Arial&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12px;&quot;&gt;About ShopCart&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;\r\n&lt;div&gt;\r\n	&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12px; color: rgb(60, 60, 59); font-family: Verdana, Arial;&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;ShopCart&lt;/b&gt; is a very powerful Open Cart theme which suits both store owners who want nice looking, easy to customise theme and developers, who are looking for a powerful, easy to customize solution for their customers. Even if you have no knowledge about programming, editing themes or HTML / CSS you will be able to change your store appearance in no time! All that thanks to our advanced, powerful option panel which allows you &lt;b&gt;to change not only elements colours, but also change theme&amp;rsquo;s backgrounds, upload your own full size image background or your own pattern!&lt;/b&gt; And if you need more customisation options, we put into this theme support for almost 200 Google fonts which can be easily selected through drop down menu!&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;div&gt;\r\n	&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;div&gt;\r\n	&lt;font color=&quot;#3c3c3b&quot; face=&quot;Verdana, Arial&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12px;&quot;&gt;This theme also comes with its own, &lt;b&gt;custom footer module&lt;/b&g