(182, 31, 'Shoppa - Multi-Purpose OpenCart Theme', '&lt;h2&gt;\r\n	&lt;font color=&quot;#3c3c3b&quot; face=&quot;Verdana, Arial&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12px;&quot;&gt;About&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;\r\n&lt;div&gt;\r\n	&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;div&gt;\r\n	&lt;font color=&quot;#3c3c3b&quot; face=&quot;Verdana, Arial&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12px;&quot;&gt;Shoppa is a multi-purpose ecommerce theme and template. It can be used on any opencart store.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;div&gt;\r\n	&lt;font color=&quot;#3c3c3b&quot; face=&quot;Verdana, Arial&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12px;&quot;&gt;It supports all the OpenCart features such as:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;div&gt;\r\n	&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;div&gt;\r\n	&lt;table style=&quot;font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-size: 13px; background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246); width: 646px;&quot;&gt;\r\n		&lt;tbody&gt;\r\n			&lt;tr&gt;\r\n				&lt;td style=&quot;line-height: 18px; width: 318px;&quot;&gt;\r\n					&lt;ul&gt;\r\n						&lt;li&gt;\r\n							Open Source&lt;/li&gt;\r\n						&lt;li&gt;\r\n							Documentation&lt;/li&gt;\r\n						&lt;li&gt;\r\n							Unlimited Categories&lt;/li&gt;\r\n						&lt;li&gt;\r\n							Unlimited Products&lt;/li&gt;\r\n						&lt;li&gt;\r\n							Unlimited Manufacturers&lt;/li&gt;\r\n						&lt;li&gt;\r\n							Templatable&lt;/li&gt;\r\n						&lt;li&gt;\r\n							Multi-Language&lt;/li&gt;\r\n						&lt;li&gt;\r\n							Multi-Currency&lt;/li&gt;\r\n						&lt;li&gt;\r\n							Product Reviews&lt;/li&gt;\r\n						&lt;li&gt;\r\n							Product Ratings&lt;/li&gt;\r\n						&lt;li&gt;\r\n							Downloadable Products&lt;/li&gt;\r\n						&lt;li&gt;\r\n							PCI Compliant&lt;/li&gt;\r\n					&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n				&lt;/td&gt;\r\n				&lt;td style=&quot;line-height: 18px;&quot;&gt;\r\n					&lt;ul&gt;\r\n						&lt;li&gt;\r\n							Automatic Image Resizing&lt;/li&gt;\r\n						&lt;li&gt;\r\n							Multiple Tax Rates&lt;/li&gt;\r\n						&lt;li&gt;\r\n							Related Products&lt;/li&gt;\r\n						&lt;li&gt;\r\n							Unlimited Information Pages&lt;/li&gt;\r\n						&lt;li&gt;\r\n							Shipping Weight Calculation&lt;/li&gt;\r\n						&lt;li&gt;\r\n							Discount Coupon System&lt;/li&gt;\r\n						&lt;li&gt;\r\n							Search Engine Optimization (SEO)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n						&lt;li&gt;\r\n							Unlimited Module Instance System&lt;/li&gt;\r\n						&lt;li&gt;\r\n							Backup &amp;amp; Restore Tools&lt;/li&gt;\r\n						&lt;li&gt;\r\n							Printable Invoices&lt;/li&gt;\r\n						&lt;li&gt;\r\n							Sales Reports&lt;/li&gt;\r\n						&lt;li&gt;\r\n							Error Logging&lt;/li&gt;\r\n					&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n				&lt;/td&gt;\r\n			&lt;/tr&gt;\r\n		&lt;/tbody&gt;\r\n	&lt;/table&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;div&gt;\r\n	&lt;h2&gt;\r\n		Features&lt;/h2&gt;\r\n	&lt;div&gt;\r\n		&lt;ul&gt;\r\n			&lt;li&gt;\r\n				Responsive design &amp;ndash; Support for hand-held devices (See Demo). Can be set ON/OFF in admin backend&lt;/li&gt;\r\n			&lt;li&gt;\r\n				Responsive banners lideshow plugin &amp;ndash; easy to integrate and displays well on all devices&lt;/li&gt;\r\n			&lt;li&gt;\r\n				Responsive product carousel for featured products &amp;ndash; you can add unlimited number of featured products&lt;/li&gt;\r\n			&lt;li&gt;\r\n				Clean HTML 5 , CSS3 and well commented code &amp;ndash; easy to customize and modify&lt;/li&gt;\r\n			&lt;li&gt;\r\n				Pinterest button for product image sharing on Pinterest.com. It helps to generate traffic to your website&lt;/li&gt;\r\n			&lt;li&gt;\r\n				Background image uploader and manager. Supports different image sizes&lt;/li&gt;\r\n			&lt;li&gt;\r\n				Admin panel to manage the theme options and settings (Unbranded)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n			&lt;li&gt;\r\n				Cloud Zoom integratration &amp;ndash; It helps to magnify the product images&lt;/li&gt;\r\n			&lt;li&gt;\r\n				ColorBox Zoom &amp;ndash; It helps to zoom-in popup product images in a popup&lt;/li&gt;\r\n			&lt;li&gt;\r\n				Social media integration. You can add your Facebook, Twitter, Google Plus and Pinterest profiles&lt;/li&gt;\r\n			&lt;li&gt;\r\n				Unbranded &amp;ndash; No link back top our website so you are free to add your own brand name&lt;/li&gt;\r\n			&lt;li&gt;\r\n				Clean and result oriented product &amp;ndash; Product page is clean and has no clutter&lt;/li&gt;\r\n			&lt;li&gt;\r\n				Google fonts integration for headers &amp;ndash; You are free to choose your favorite fonts without having to download them&lt;/li&gt;\r\n			&lt;li&gt;\r\n				Well documented installation manual&lt;/li&gt;\r\n			&lt;li&gt;\r\n				Modern design with valid coding which incorporates modern technologies of web development e.g, Modernizr, Respond.js, Normalize&lt;/li&gt;\r\n			&lt;li&gt;\r\n				Unique design and layout. It also supports multiple layouts&lt;/li&gt;\r\n			&lt;li&gt;\r\n				Cross-browser compatible &amp;ndash; IE8 , IE9, IE10 , Firefox 3, Firefox 4, Safari 4, Safari 5, Chrome, Opera&lt;/li&gt;\r\n			&lt;li&gt;\r\n				No core files have been edited manually. This ensures that there is no interferance with other modules on your store&lt;/li&gt;\r\n		&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;/div&gt;\r\n	&lt;div&gt;\r\n		All modified files have been listed in the installation manual and theme documentation.&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n', '/items/2012/12/182/Shoppa Store.png', '/items/2012/12/182/Shoppa Store.png', '/items/2012/12/182/22ceb515d6f0be69921cbbb9cfc521f6.zip', '/items/2012/12/182/22ceb515d6f0be69921cbbb9cfc521f6.zip', 'Shoppa Store.zip', NULL, 'http://sokothemes.com/themes/opencart/shoppa/layout1/index.php', 40, 40, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'false', 'false', '0000-00-00', '0000-00-00', '', '2012-12-11 16:56:45', 'active', 'themes', '', '', 0),
(187, 31, 'Ultimo - Fluid Responsive Magento Theme', '&lt;div style=&quot;color: rgb(60, 60, 59); font-family: Verdana, Arial; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; line-height: normal;&quot;&gt;Ultimo is a premium Magento theme with &lt;b&gt;advanced admin module&lt;/b&gt;. Itâ€™s extremely customizable, easy to use and fully responsive. Suitable for every type of store. Great as a starting point for your custom projects.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;color: rgb(60, 60, 59); font-family: Verdana, Arial; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; line-height: normal;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: normal;&quot;&gt;Compatible with Magento: &lt;/span&gt;&lt;b&gt;1.5.x&lt;/b&gt; (1.5.0.1, 1.5.1.0), &lt;b&gt;1.6.x&lt;/b&gt; (1.6.0.0, 1.6.1.0, 1.6.2.0), &lt;b&gt;1.7.x&lt;/b&gt; (1.7.0.0, 1.7.0.1, 1.7.0.2)&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;color: rgb(60, 60, 59); font-family: Verdana, Arial; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; line-height: normal;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 style=&quot;color: rgb(60, 60, 59); font-family: Verdana, Arial; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; line-height: normal;&quot;&gt;Customizable design&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;color: rgb(60, 60, 59); font-family: Verdana, Arial; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; line-height: normal;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;color: rgb(60, 60, 59); font-family: Verdana, Arial; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; line-height: normal;&quot;&gt;&lt;div&gt;You have never seen so many options! You can change the visual appearance of almost every element of the design. Your imagination is your only limit.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;Change colors of almost 50 elements using color pickers, apply textures for header, footer and for the entire page, upload background image and configure its properties (position, repeating,