(186, 31, 'Fortis - flexible Magento Theme', '&lt;div style=&quot;color: rgb(60, 60, 59); font-family: Verdana, Arial; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; line-height: normal; font-weight: normal;&quot;&gt;\r\n	Fortis is a high quality Magento theme with administrative module, suitable for every type of store. It was designed with focus on user experience and usability, to make Magento shopping quick, easy and fun.&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;div style=&quot;color: rgb(60, 60, 59); font-family: Verdana, Arial; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; line-height: normal; font-weight: normal;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;div style=&quot;color: rgb(60, 60, 59); font-family: Verdana, Arial; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; line-height: normal;&quot;&gt;\r\n	Compatible with Magento: &lt;b&gt;1.5.0.1, 1.5.1.0, 1.6.0.0, 1.6.1.0, 1.6.2.0, 1.7.0.0, 1.7.0.1, 1.7.0.2&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;div style=&quot;color: rgb(60, 60, 59); font-family: Verdana, Arial; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; line-height: normal;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;div style=&quot;color: rgb(60, 60, 59); font-family: Verdana, Arial; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; line-height: normal;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;div&gt;\r\n		Fortis is equipped with the&lt;b&gt; dedicated administrative module, &lt;/b&gt;which brings all the features necessary for successful webstore &amp;ndash; all at the command of a few key strokes. With&lt;b&gt; extensive user guide &lt;/b&gt;which will help you configure your store in a few minutes.&lt;/div&gt;\r\n	&lt;div&gt;\r\n		&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n	&lt;div&gt;\r\n		Fortis isn&amp;rsquo;t a sub-theme of the Magento &amp;ldquo;default&amp;rdquo; theme. It&amp;rsquo;s &lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: bold;&quot;&gt;a standalone design package&lt;/span&gt; with its own theme and skins. You can easily create your own sub-themes. Basic design